title: ‘Survivor’ Season 43, Episode 6
description:
Tyson and Riley are joined by former ‘Survivor’ contestant Desi Williams to discuss Episode 6 of Season 43. They talk about the start of the merging of the tribes, the much-anticipated confrontation between Elie and Gabler, and what it takes to effectively lie on ‘Survivor.’

Hosts: Tyson Apostol and Riley McAtee
Guest: Desi Williams
Producers: Jessie Lopez and Kai Grady
